    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/e19e6426924562d25306fd5bba85f226.poster.avif?t=1772334775\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/e19e6426924562d25306fd5bba85f226.webm?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/e19e6426924562d25306fd5bba85f226.mp4?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Powerplay》中，你要管理一个工业国家的经济和军事战略。确保捍卫自己的资产并征服新的土地。在有限而无情的《Powerplay》世界中，定义自己的生存之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/fd398c11a5208796a23ae5ad2e6fff31.webp?t=1772334775\" width=750 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/8c7811a1465a0790645ac75c1bc6e3b2.poster.avif?t=1772334775\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/8c7811a1465a0790645ac75c1bc6e3b2.webm?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/8c7811a1465a0790645ac75c1bc6e3b2.mp4?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你开发的资源和技术来建造、装备和部署庞大的军队。扩张领土或保卫据点。从选择生产哪种武器到善用地形和补给线，每一个决定都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/c8345d061228d9efdade6bf6013fddf3.webp?t=1772334775\" width=750 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/1062b020576ac0b13a65ce083a9a81db.poster.avif?t=1772334775\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/1062b020576ac0b13a65ce083a9a81db.webm?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/1062b020576ac0b13a65ce083a9a81db.mp4?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立高效的供应链是《Powerplay》的核心玩法。设计并优化传送带网络，将原材料运送到工厂，再在那里转化为中间资源和武器。挑战在于平衡资源分配和空间管理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/cfe91c9f0cd2366ca013bdc2ac53d068.webp?t=1772334775\" width=750 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/a1605215fcfc399c4f1f08393324c3c9.poster.avif?t=1772334775\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/a1605215fcfc399c4f1f08393324c3c9.webm?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010280/extras/a1605215fcfc399c4f1f08393324c3c9.mp4?t=1772334775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏的一个核心特色在于资源局部性。游戏中没有全球库存。你必须战略性地开采、加工和运输资源以扩大你的基地，还要建立补给线并保护它们，才能维持对土地的控制。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拥有数百个单位的经典即时战略战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ‌等距视角</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 传送带</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 战争迷雾机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持高程的地形编辑器</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >称霸全球</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandbox</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Military</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用周边资源制造枪支</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 制造坦克以突破敌对定居点</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 核武器</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transport</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用工人和传送带进行短距离运输</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用车辆进行中距离运输</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用火车进行长距离运输</p></li>[/list开采和提炼铀，解锁能够扭转乾坤的武器。这是一个漫长的过程，在这个过程中，你很容易受到致命的干扰。不过，如果你能有效控制核生产，将在游戏后期拥有巨大优势。t游戏模式t]</ul>",
